'''Beyond Bree''' was a calendar produced by the [[American Mensa Tolkien Special Interest Group]] between [[1985]] and [[1994]], with only [[1990]] and [[1993]] being exceptions; printing resumed in [[2010]]. Early issues were variously edited by [[Carl F. Hostetter]], [[Nancy Martsch]], and [[Steve Deyo]], while the issues stemming from the recent revival of the series has been edited exclusively by Daniel Smith.
